<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "Friendium" %></title>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kurale|ABeeZee" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= javascript_include_tag "vendor/modernizr" %>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application' %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>

  <body>

    <div class="sign_in_bar">

      <div id="myModal" class="reveal-modal" data-reveal aria-labelledby="modalTitle" aria-hidden="true" role="dialog">
        <h2 id="modalTitle">Welcome to Friendium!</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Friendium is an app designed to help you keep track of your many friendships. To get started, click the add friend square and add a new friendship. Once your friendship is created, go ahead and click the handshake to start recording interactions with your friend. You can enter the interaction type, the date of the interaction, and detailed notes you want to remeber. Once you've added interactions you can click on the heart icon on each friend tile to see a breakdown of you interactions by type. If you make a mistake anywhere along the way, you can use the pen and paper icon to edit, or you can start fresh by using the trash icon. 
        </p>
        <p></p>
        <a class="close-reveal-modal" aria-label="Close">&#215;</a>
      </div>

      <ul id="sign_in_ul">
      <% if current_user  %>
        <li class="link"> <%= link_to "Logout", logout_path %> <a class="getting-started" href="#" data-reveal-id="myModal">Getting started!</a></li>
      <% else %>
        <li class="link"><%= link_to "Sign in with Google", "/auth/google" %></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <%= yield %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
  </body>
</html>
